# 🌐 Riya Patel's Developer Portfolio

Welcome to my personal portfolio website – a modern, responsive, and cleanly designed web app built with **React** to showcase my projects, experience, skills, and achievements as a Software Engineer.
---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Area         | Technologies Used                        |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Frontend     | React.js, Tailwind CSS, JavaScript        |
| Animations   | Framer Motion                             |
| Icons        | React Icons, Tabler Icons                 |
| Hosting      | GitHub Pages / Vercel / Netlify (choose one) |

---

## ✨ Features

- 📱 Fully responsive across all devices
- 🎨 Clean, minimal UI with smooth animations
- 🧠 Sectioned layout: About, Skills, Projects, Experience, Contact
- 💬 Dynamic contact form (optional email integration)
- 🛠️ Easy to customize for your own use

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

```bash
My_Portfolio/
├── public/
│   └── images, favicon, preview assets
├── src/
│   ├── components/       # Reusable components (Navbar, Footer, etc.)
│   ├── pages/            # Main sections like About, Projects, etc.
│   ├── assets/           # Icons, logos, illustrations
│   ├── App.js            # Main app structure
│   └── index.js          # Entry point
└── tailwind.config.js    # Tailwind configuration
